title: Israeli forces push deep into Gaza City amid ‘catastrophic’ struggles at hospitals
description: Hospitals in Gaza City reported dwindling supplies of fuel, water and power as fighting raged outside.

title: U.S. is warned about its global standing as Gaza suffering persists
description: Arab leaders admonished Secretary of State Antony Blinken, saying the U.S. will be deemed complicit for civilian deaths in Israel’s unrestrained Gaza assault.

title: War in Gaza has some posting more than ever. Others are going dark.
description: A month into the Israel-Gaza war, an adjacent battle has taken shape on social media, shifting the norms on platforms where millions spend much of their days.

title: Israel-Gaza war live updates: Gaza hospitals under bombardment as medical system reaches point of ‘no return’
description: The International Committee of the Red Cross warned that thousands of civilian lives were at risk. Israel says Hamas is using hospitals to store supplies and fuel.

title: Hamas antitank strikes show depth of ‘powerful’ arsenal facing Israel
description: Hamas has spent years boosting its firepower to include antitank missiles and other arms. Israel, said one military expert, faces “a much more powerful Hamas.”
